{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_05_04",
  "title": "サニーピース 05 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "そう……大変だったのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… It must have been so hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、手術は成功したけど\n元気になるにはそこからが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ the surgery was a success‚ but\ngetting healthy from that point on was…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "大きな手術と長い入院生活で体の機能が衰えてたから\nリハビリには凄く苦労して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My body was so weak from the major surgery and long hospital stay\nthat I really struggled with rehab…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "それに、来年には高校受験も控えてたから\n勉強の遅れも取り戻さなきゃいけなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ I had high school entrance exams the following year‚\nso I had to make up for my late studies as well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4895357974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "リハビリと受験勉強の両立か……\nそれは大変そうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Balancing rehab and studying for exams…\nThat sounds incredibly tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "事情が事情だ。現役合格にこだわらずに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Given the circumstances‚ you didn't have to insist on passing the first time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9592280944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "高校受験を一年遅らせても良かったんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wouldn't it have been okay to delay high school for a year?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "両親もそう言ってくれたんですけど……やりたいことが\n沢山あったから、一年も足踏みしたくなかったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My parents said so too… but there were so many things\nI wanted to do‚ I didn't want to stay in place for a whole year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 53.192901953
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 53.192901953
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 55.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 61.8923258577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "いち……に……いち……に……\nはぁ、はぁ……あとちょっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One… two… one… two…\nPant‚ pant… Just a little more…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8923258577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "看護師",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nurse",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "大丈夫、さくらちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you okay‚ Sakura-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.4540583848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "看護師",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nurse",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "苦しかったら、そろそろ休憩しても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's too much‚ you can take a break now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 73.3354642788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、まだやれます……\n1、2、1、2……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I can still keep going…\nOne‚ two‚ one‚ two…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "（強がってみたけど……本当はとっくに限界……）\n（足がふらついて、真っ直ぐ歩けないよ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I tried to act tough… but honestly‚ I'm already at my limit…）\n（My legs are shaking so much I can't walk straight…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 90.7017459948
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 99.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "（息が苦しい……体が痛い……足に力が入らない……）\n（こんなに辛いのに……こんなに頑張ってるのに……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I can't breathe… my body hurts… my legs have no strength…）\n（It's so painful… and I'm working so hard…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 104.7856006701
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "（本当に、体は良くなってるのかな？　本当に、運動）\n（出来るようになるのかな？　元気に……なれるかな？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Is my body really getting better? Will I really）\n（be able to move again? Can I… become healthy?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4737878013,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 120.7609974305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……きゃっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant‚ pant… Kyah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7609974305,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3399.998934999999,
          "startTime": 124.1609963655
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 124.1609963655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "看護師",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nurse",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さくらちゃん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1609963655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "看護師",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nurse",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "無理しないで少し休みましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't push yourself‚ let's take a little rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 128.3816993157
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "（私だって休みたいよ。どうして私ばっかり）\n（こんなに目にあわなきゃいけないんだろう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I want to rest too. Why do I have to）\n（be the only one going through such a hard time…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 136.4249419291
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "（リハビリなんてもう嫌、こんなに辛いんだから）\n（ここでやめたって誰も文句言わないよね？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I hate this rehab‚ it's so miserable）\n（No one would complain if I quit here‚ right?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.9333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 146.0388646841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "（健康になれなくても、一生運動が出来なくても）\n（私が引きこもって何もしなければいいんだから……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even if I don't get healthy‚ even if I can never exercise again‚）\n（it's fine as long as I stay shut in and do nothing…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.5666656494,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_heart-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3935.5319103,
          "startTime": 155.5021975597
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 155.5021975597
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ドクン",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Thump",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.5021975597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 156.7021975597
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "（あ……今、心臓がドクンって鳴った……）\n（まるで、弱気な私を応援してるみたい……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ah… my heart just gave a thump…）\n（Like it's cheering for my weak self…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_heart-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4985.245108599997,
          "startTime": 168.8519117753
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_heart-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5900.009155299984,
          "startTime": 169.766675822
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "（ドクンドクン……心臓が頑張れって言ってる……）\n（負けるなって私を励ましてる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thump-thump… my heart is telling me to hang in there…）\n（Encouraging me not to give up…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.0333414714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 182.66211555
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "……大丈夫です\nもうちょっとだけやらせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm okay.\nPlease let me do just a little more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.700008138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "看護師",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nurse",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え……でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.5921607415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 191.1282377322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
