      "text": "……友ちゃん、久しぶり。元気だった？\nって、お墓の前で言うのも変だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Tomo-chan‚ long time no see. How have you been?\nIt's a bit strange to say that in front of a grave.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.4333414714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 255.9380366563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
