      "text": "私は元気だよ\n見て、この制服。私、高校生になったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm doing great.\nLook at this uniform. I've become a high school student.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.900008138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_05_04-skr024.m4a",
      "text": "毎日学校に通って、普通の子達と同じように勉強したり\n運動したりしてるんだよ。信じられないよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I go to school every day and study just like normal kids\nand exercise too. You wouldn't believe it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.8666748047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 273.9221858103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
