      "text": "大変なこともあるけど、そういう時はこの胸が\nいつも大切なことを教えてくれるの。凄いでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are tough times too‚ but when that happens‚ my heart\nalways teaches me what's important. It's amazing‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.900008138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
