      "text": "『やりたかったリスト』も消化してるよ\n友ちゃんの分までやり尽くすから、ちゃんと見ててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm checking off my \"Things I Wanted to Try List\" too.\nI'll do enough for both of us‚ so please keep watching me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 286.3747545095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
