      "text": "お盆だから、お墓参りに来てる人が沢山いるなぁ\nまあ、私もその一人なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it's Obon‚ there are so many people visiting graves.\nWell‚ I'm one of them too…",
