      "text": "さっきの声は、あそこの綺麗な人が言ったのかな？\n誰かのお墓参りをしてるみたいだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was that voice from that beautiful person over there?\nShe seems to be visiting someone's grave…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.1667053223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 334.0584735631
    },
    {
