      "text": "あら？\nあなた、もしかして、麻奈ちゃんのファンかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh?\nAre you‚ by any chance‚ a fan of Mana-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.2000386556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
