      "text": "そのお墓、お花がいくつもお供えされてますけど\n沢山の人に好かれている方だったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That grave has so many flowers offered to it.\nWas she someone loved by many people?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 356.1667053223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
